name: Seed Bearing Herbs #2
description:
The text in this art is from the Akashic Records; it's the original intended translation from spirit. We know the biblical version of Genesis 1:30 is a gross mistranslation because other animals cannot read, and therefore do not need a line in a book transcribed to them.

In order to create peace on earth, we must be peaceful on earth. 

There is only one being... You. That cow is just you in cow form. Do unto others as we would have them do unto us, if the roles were reversed.
